    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Panaches worn on the head, made up of many quetzal feathers. Literally "quetzal-feather hair" in Nahuatl.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
